# Artificial Intelligence (AI) - Introduction Project

## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

This project provides a comprehensive introduction to **Artificial Intelligence**, covering what AI is, its real-world applications, and two detailed case studies. It's designed for students, learners, and anyone curious about AI technology.

### What's Included:
- âœ… Definition and characteristics of Artificial Intelligence
- âœ… 8 major uses and applications of AI
- âœ… Case Study 1: Self-Driving Cars (how AI powers autonomous vehicles)
- âœ… Case Study 2: AI in Smartphones (practical AI features you use daily)
- âœ… Links to educational videos for deeper learning
- âœ… High-quality images illustrating AI concepts
- âœ… Interactive HTML webpage
- âœ… PDF version for offline reading
- âœ… PowerPoint presentation for classroom use

