## ğŸš€ How to View the Project

### Option 1: View Interactive Website (Recommended)
1. Download or clone the repository
2. **Open `index.html`** in any web browser (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge)
3. Click through the navigation tabs to explore sections
4. Click video links to access learning resources
5. Works on desktop, tablet, and mobile devices

### Option 2: View GitHub Pages (Online)
1. Go to your GitHub repository
2. Navigate to **Settings â†’ Pages**
3. Select **main branch** as source
4. Your project will be live at: `https://your-username.github.io/ai-introduction-project`
5. Share this link with anyone to view online

### Option 3: View PDF Version
1. Open **`AI_Project.pdf`** with any PDF reader
2. Perfect for offline reading and printing
3. Can be emailed to teachers or classmates

### Option 4: View PowerPoint Presentation
1. Open **`AI_Project.pptx`** with Microsoft PowerPoint, Google Slides, or LibreOffice
2. Ideal for classroom presentations
3. Full-screen mode for delivering to an audience

