## ğŸ“¸ Image Folder (`images/`)

The `images/` folder should contain visuals for:

| Image | Purpose | Download From |
|-------|---------|-----------------|
| **ai-concept.png** | General AI illustration | Freepik, Unsplash, Pixabay |
| **ai-robot.png** | Robot or AI character | Freepik, Pixabay |
| **self-driving-car.png** | Autonomous vehicle with sensors | Unsplash, Pixabay |
| **smartphone-ai.png** | Phone with face recognition | Freepik, Unsplash |
| **chatbot-ai.png** | Chat interface or virtual assistant | Freepik, Pixabay |
| **computer-vision.png** | Image recognition visualization | Unsplash, Pixabay |
| **machine-learning.png** | Neural network or data visualization | Freepik, Pixabay |
| **neural-network.png** | Brain or network diagram | Freepik, Unsplash |

### Free Image Resources:
- **Freepik** (www.freepik.com) - Search "artificial intelligence", "robot", "autonomous car"
- **Unsplash** (www.unsplash.com) - Search "AI technology", "robot", "smartphone"
- **Pixabay** (www.pixabay.com) - Free stock images, search "machine learning"
- **Pexels** (www.pexels.com) - Royalty-free, search "AI", "technology"
- **Pixelated** (www.pixelated.co.uk) - AI-generated illustrations

**Tip:** Download images with descriptive names matching the list above. Use PNG or JPG format, preferably 800x600px or larger for quality.

