## ğŸ“ File Descriptions

### index.html
**What it is:** Interactive website with tab-based navigation  
**How to use:** Double-click to open in browser  
**Best for:** Interactive exploration and classroom demos  
**Size:** ~25 KB  

### AI_Project.pdf
**What it is:** Professional PDF document with all content  
**How to use:** Open with any PDF reader (Adobe, built-in viewer)  
**Best for:** Offline reading, printing, sharing via email  
**Size:** ~2-3 MB  

### AI_Project.pptx
**What it is:** PowerPoint presentation with organized slides  
**How to use:** Open with Microsoft PowerPoint, Google Slides, or LibreOffice  
**Best for:** Classroom presentations, teacher presentations  
**Size:** ~5-8 MB  

### README.md
**What it is:** Documentation and guide (this file)  
**How to use:** Displays on GitHub repository homepage  
**Best for:** Understanding the project structure  
**Size:** ~8 KB  

### video-link.txt
**What it is:** Curated list of YouTube learning resources  
**How to use:** Open with any text editor, click or copy links  
**Best for:** Finding additional learning materials  
**Size:** ~2 KB  

### images/ folder
**What it is:** Storage for AI concept images  
**How to use:** Add PNG/JPG images with descriptive names  
**Best for:** Visual representation in HTML and PDF  
**Size:** Varies (recommend ~500 KB - 2 MB total)  

